traefik.http.routers.http-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.middlewares=redirect-to-https
traefik.http.routers.http-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.rule=Host(`ecard.ashbi.ca`) && PathPrefix(`/`)
traefik.http.routers.http-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.service=http-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088
traefik.http.routers.https-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.entryPoints=https
traefik.http.routers.https-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.middlewares=gzip
traefik.http.routers.https-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.rule=Host(`ecard.ashbi.ca`) && PathPrefix(`/`)
traefik.http.routers.https-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.service=https-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088
traefik.http.routers.https-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.tls.certresolver=letsencrypt
traefik.http.routers.https-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.tls=true
traefik.http.services.http-0-x8okwogw0so8s08oss04s088.loadbalancer.server.port=3000

caddy_0.try_files={path} /index.html /index.php
caddy_0=https://ecard.ashbi.ca
